> Error	1	error C2610: 'spdlog::details::async_log_helper::async_msg::async_msg(spdlog::details::async_log_helper::async_msg &&)' : is not a special member function which can be defaulted	c:\work\logging\spdtry\dev\include\spdlog\details\async_log_helper.h	66	1	dev


